## STEP 4 — Screenshot Your Dashboard

Before writing the README you need screenshots. Take one screenshot per Power BI page:

- Open Power BI → go to each page
- Press `Windows + Shift + S` → select the full canvas area
- Save each to:
```
outputs/dashboard/page1_executive_summary.png
outputs/dashboard/page2_customer_segments.png
outputs/dashboard/page3_product_payment.png
outputs/dashboard/page4_ml_performance.png
outputs/dashboard/page5_customer_behaviour.png
outputs/dashboard/page6_retention_actions.png